Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候沒能救你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要向我道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本無需道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便要付出生命的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想弄清陛下的真實想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你在隱瞞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你可得想清楚再做決定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是喜歡夏利歐斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百列大人情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼叫都沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直把自己關在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾之後又是貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然連索菲大人也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近恐怖攻擊太頻繁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 越獄犯有可能還藏在王都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚嚇人的紅龍還在到處飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭結束了也不太平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說今晚王宮還要舉辦舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,權貴們這種時候還過得這麼瀟灑 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒查到下落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵的數量也很多 調查很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜和巴卡斯他們也沒有任何消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚有紅龍在亞納提上空飛來飛去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就這點傳聞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個龍是什麼顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顏色？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得…好像說很紅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜能變身成紅龍 她是龍族的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 請讓我也出去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾應該跟妮娜在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日落之後 士兵數量就會減少了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你能一直待在我身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 首先讓貴族少爺和妮娜潛入王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛入王宮後 一旦找到國王就在附近待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸頭就跟這個大個子大叔一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從騎士團宿舍潛入王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒是團長 阿薩謝爾則是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醉鬼是神對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就只能你上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 確認爆炸頭潛入王宮之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就發送信號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你就變成龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要搞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能搞事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要引起混亂就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁亂把國王的手鐲搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後騎在妮娜背上從陽台逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會這麼順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要妮娜變成龍就不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被抓了 我還會去監獄接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至於剩下的人 萬一他們沒能成功逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時你們就負責保障逃離路線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再做好對付追兵的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得在逃離路線上待命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑兵來了的話還得靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿薩謝爾 他就交給你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話 這就是個看著很犀利的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切忌勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的行動全看我的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 她到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 小妹妹她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常想接潛入王宮的任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八成只是想吃王宮料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知另一邊順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子你很熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也是拿過騎士稱號的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是的是十年前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 跟你的團長一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退路就交給你保障囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙應該沒辦法變成龍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們漆黑兵 將生命徹底獻給了國王您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懇請陛下專心履行使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上到舞會時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下明白您的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今上一場戰爭的復興舉步維艱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參加集資活動也是國王的重要職責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨 你這個樣子會被懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 我就只是在吃而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位不是維斯彭迪家族的亞歷山大少爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是很久沒在這種場合碰面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 嘛 哈 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位女性是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那什麼 這位女性是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是位佳人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 亞山大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說你在叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幫女人在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們在等待國王的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀請她們幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等一下等一下等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利歐斯王要跳舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是頭一回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 剛才是不是那名女性邀請的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺 你的未婚妻邀請國王跳舞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她啊…其實是我妹妹來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要怎樣才會跟國王跳起舞來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那種舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說之前跳的那種很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過剛才那種也好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好 還有事要問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 肚子痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我闖什麼禍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能再見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你無法見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定全心全意地履行國王的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說好了嗎 今天告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事跟你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才不是還陪我跳舞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時你都吻我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說要全告訴我嗎 難道是騙我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 全是騙你的 還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不退下 我就叫士兵抓你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你還真是個狠心男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好歹也是我徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能麻煩你少傷害點她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師…師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把戴在左手的手鐲交來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西只要戴上了到死才能取下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼把手砍下來 要麼去死 國王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個國王今後依然可能殺害大量生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就先射你 再殺掉夏利歐斯如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餘興到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵很快就到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罷 今晚我們就先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不能一起跳舞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能 永遠不能了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你別傷害她了 國王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下 您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微悠哉了點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給大家發信號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺 您的妹妹被捲入紛爭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？啊 我去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該還沒走遠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守好後門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賊人還在王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放跑他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 晚點再消沉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在必須趕緊逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在必須趕緊逃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等 跑太快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想再跟他們扯上關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 回家好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那什麼 我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貧民街在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德·達克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 妮娜 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別以為這種小伎倆每次都有用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是紅龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得死在這
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利歐斯17世起得很早
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他獨自一人想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神擊的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從天堂到地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 來吃肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真喜歡肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週也要看哦
